# Force LF for digest-input file types so contentSha256 / tree digests are
# stable across platforms (CRLF checkouts must not drift runtime digests).
# Matches the inputs hashed by scripts/runtime-tree-digest.mjs for adapters
# and related release content.
*.sh text eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.mjs text eol=lf
*.ts text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.jsonl text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.svg text eol=lf
